}{}$${\rm{LRI}} = 100\left({z + {{{t_{Ri}}-{t_{Rz}}} \over {{t_{R\left({Z + 1} \right)}}-{t_{Rz}}}}} \right)$$\end{document}LRI=100(z+tRi−tRztR(Z+1)−tRz)
Within this context, a generalized form for the LRI is shown in Eq. (3):
(3)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
\usepackage{amsmath}
\usepackage{wasysym} 
\usepackage{amsfonts} 
\usepackage{amssymb} 
\usepackage{amsbsy}
\usepackage{upgreek}
